<section id="process">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="process-header fade-up">
      <p class="section-label">How it works</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">From vision to <em>finished piece</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="process-steps">
      <div class="process-step fade-up">
        <div class="step-number">01</div>
        <h3 class="step-title">Reach Out</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">
          Send a message, share some photos, and tell me what you have in mind.
          We'll set up a time to chat.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step fade-up fade-up-delay-1">
        <div class="step-number">02</div>
        <h3 class="step-title">Consultation</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">
          We meet in person or virtually to go over the details — measurements,
          fabric, timeline, and budget.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step fade-up fade-up-delay-2">
        <div class="step-number">03</div>
        <h3 class="step-title">Creation</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">
          I get to work. You'll receive updates along the way,
          and we'll do a fitting to ensure everything is right.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step fade-up fade-up-delay-3">
        <div class="step-number">04</div>
        <h3 class="step-title">Delivery</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">
          Your finished piece is ready for collection.
          Wear it with joy — it was made just for you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
